1.BEM la gi:
    la tieu chuan dat ten Class khi viet CSS
2. Tai sao phai dung BEM:
    Khi lam mot du an lon theo team thi moi nguoi dat class mot ten 
    member dat class trung nhau co the gay sai code, CSS de len nhau.
3. Y nghia:
    viet tat cua Block Element Modifier
    Block: khoi
    Elemet: thanh phan trong khoi
    Modified: bo sung y nghia cho "Block" hoac "Khoi"
4. Cu phap:
    .block
    .block__element
    .block--modifier
    .block__element--modifier
5. Ung Dung:
    xay dung layout web size
    xay dung thanh phan tren web size
6. Uu Diem:
    Tinh ro rang
    Giup ca team lam viec voi nhau de dang
    Tinh Module, khong lo CSS cua class nay anh huong len CSS cua class khac
7. Nhuoc Diem:
    Ten Class dai
    Mot so nguoi cho la xau
8. Khi nao dung BEM la phu hop:
    Du an nhieu Members
    Du an lon
